GTG for now.

::Zardus::

Zardus nods. "Good."

He comes to a stop near a door, pressing a button near it. The door opens, 
revealing a small room. Having been made on the planet, the Alliance base 
didn't have too many conforts, and big spacious quarters was one on the ones 
it was lacking.

"One of you can use this as quarters," he says, looking at the two bots, "Or 
both of you."
